title: Will Forte
description:
Actor and writer Will Forte feels honored about being Conan O’Brien’s friend.

Will sits down with Conan to discuss getting married and becoming a father, overcoming “writer’s brain” during his time on SNL, reviving MacGruber with the new Peacock series, and teaming up with Val Kilmer to get on The Amazing Race. Later, Conan gives his cool-guy persona another honest attempt.

 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.

 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
